io.github.u004.uwutils

Class UwMap

  • java.lang.Object
    • io.github.u004.uwutils.UwMap

  • public final class UwMap
extends Object
    An object mapping utility.

    UwMap is the utility class that provide functionality to create maps based on the instance fields. Highly usable for enum types.

    Since:
    0.1.0
